# SingleCourseWebApp Template Documentation

This document provides a comprehensive guide to the template files in the SingleCourseWebApp Django application, including their relationships with JavaScript and CSS files. The data passed into these template files come from views.py.

## Template Structure Overview

The templates in this application follow a hierarchical structure:

```
course/templates/course/
├── adminpage/                # Admin interface templates
├── editcourse/               # Course management templates
├── homepage/                 # Home page templates
├── learningpage/             # Learning interface templates
│   └── lesson_types/         # Specific lesson type templates
└── submissions/              # Submission management templates
```

### 3. Learning Interface

#### 3.1 Learn Page

**Template:** `course/templates/course/learningpage/learn.html`

**Description:** Main learning interface for students.

**JavaScript Dependencies:**
- `course/static/course/js/learn.js`
  - Handles navigation between lessons
  - Tracks progress

**CSS Dependencies:**
- `course/static/course/css/learn.css`
  - Styling for learning interface
  - Styling for progress indicators

**Data Context:**
- `course`: Course object
- `modules`: List of module objects
- `current_module`: Currently selected module
- `progress`: User's progress object

#### 3.2 Lesson Base

**Template:** `course/templates/course/learningpage/lesson_base.html`

**Description:** Base template for all lesson types.

**JavaScript Dependencies:**
- `course/static/course/js/lesson_base.js`
  - Handles lesson completion
  - Manages navigation between lessons

**CSS Dependencies:**
- `course/static/course/css/lesson_base.css`
  - Styling for lesson layout
  - Styling for lesson navigation

**Data Context:**
- `lesson`: Current lesson object
- `next_lesson`: Next lesson object (if any)
- `prev_lesson`: Previous lesson object (if any)
- `is_completed`: Boolean indicating if lesson is completed

#### 3.3 Lesson Sidebar

**Template:** `course/templates/course/learningpage/lesson_sidebar.html`

**Description:** Sidebar navigation for lessons.

**JavaScript Dependencies:**
- `course/static/course/js/lesson_sidebar.js`
  - Handles sidebar navigation
  - Updates progress indicators

**CSS Dependencies:**
- `course/static/course/css/lesson_sidebar.css`
  - Styling for sidebar layout
  - Styling for lesson links
  - Styling for progress indicators

**Data Context:**
- `modules`: List of module objects
- `current_lesson`: Currently displayed lesson
- `lesson_progress`: Dictionary of lesson completion status

### 4. Lesson Type Templates

#### 4.1 Video Lesson

**Template:** `course/templates/course/learningpage/lesson_types/video.html`

**Description:** Template for video lessons.

**Data Context:**
- `lesson`: Lesson object with video URL

#### 4.2 Reading Lesson

**Template:** `course/templates/course/learningpage/lesson_types/reading.html`

**Description:** Template for reading lessons.

**Data Context:**
- `lesson`: Lesson object with reading content

#### 4.3 Exercise Lesson

**Template:** `course/templates/course/learningpage/lesson_types/exercise.html`

**Description:** Template for interactive exercises.

**JavaScript Dependencies:**
- `course/static/course/js/exercise.js`
  - Handles file uploads
  - Manages exercise submissions
- `course/static/course/js/file_upload.js`
  - Provides file upload functionality

**CSS Dependencies:**
- `course/static/course/css/exercise.css`
  - Styling for exercise interface
  - Styling for file upload components

**Data Context:**
- `exercise`: Exercise object with details
- `materials`: List of exercise materials
- `previous_submissions`: List of user's previous submissions